snippet.title: GeoJelly - Release Trailer - PS4 & PS5
snippet.description:
GeoJelly is a platformer where you are limited to jumping to escape the laboratory. 
PS Store: https://store.playstation.com/en-pl/product/EP6878-PPSA13253_00-0673071003693784

You'll face the challenge of accurately measuring your jumps to land where you intend to... given you endure the difficulty of the test chambers. To unlock levels you have to collect diamonds. The more diamonds the more levels you open.

#PS4 #PS5 #indiegamedev #playstation #trailer
